{"tid":2304772,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求屌醒，好想resign","createTime":"2020-11-29T05:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T15:37:31.000Z","uid":362049,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"af32dcc459a9857bcb4457e3ee6399d7cbfb4f5a","tid":2304772,"uid":362049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本來我係Part time嚟嘅，返左兩個月。咁10月尾，有個fulltime staff resign。所以呀姐問我想唔想返Fulltime，話睇下會唔會轉到做月薪，之後我答可以。隔左幾日，我再問佢，佢話上面呀姐無有new，所以未轉到monthly，照用daily rate計人工。如是者，我日日返工返到成個fulltime咁，就嚟成個月佢都無同我講過話轉月薪。日日返工返到我心灰意冷，唔係幾開心，好似被人呃咁，fg就要俾人恰咁。大家覺得佢係咪耍我？我應唔應該繼續等下？我真係唔係幾gur，好想resign但又驚揾唔到工，空白期長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2021又有一堆fg爭工"},{"pid":"ecff17753261932c10a9a9e26c888c676a040e12","tid":2304772,"uid":57073,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"parttime 返到full time 咁<br />\nd 鐘數爆晒<br />\n已經係full time"},{"pid":"02307003b454a19a08a6f3c2a7edaa25751054b7","tid":2304772,"uid":362049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecff17753261932c10a9a9e26c888c676a040e12","tid":2304772,"uid":57073,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"parttime 返到full time 咁<br />\nd 鐘數爆晒<br />\n已經係full time"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"但無fulltime人工同benefit"},{"pid":"f606ff9765c2c3f5114acaffb8f0a05f214520dd","tid":2304772,"uid":57073,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"02307003b454a19a08a6f3c2a7edaa25751054b7","tid":2304772,"uid":362049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecff17753261932c10a9a9e26c888c676a040e12","tid":2304772,"uid":57073,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"parttime 返到full time 咁<br />\nd 鐘數爆晒<br />\n已經係full time"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"但無fulltime人工同benefit"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"一般parttine段鐘計好過fulltime 喎<br />\n你份咩來...